OL,3,CTown's missing birthday cards spark
OL,4,Ccalls for Royal Mail investigation
OL,6,FBirthday cards, often with cash
OL,7,Finside, are going missing and
OL,8,Fallegedly being stolen in Penarth, an
OL,9,FITV investigation has found.
OL,11,FMum-of-two Rhian Evans, who lives in
OL,12,Fthe Vale of Glamorgan town, said she
OL,13,Ffirst noticed her post was going
OL,14,Fmissing over the summer.
OL,16,FShe said relatives sent her sons
OL,17,Fbirthday cards with money inside - but
OL,18,Fsome did not arrive.
