OL,3,CTown's missing birthday cards spark
OL,4,Ccalls for Royal Mail investigation
OL,6,FWhen she inquired about it in the
OL,7,Ftown, she realised many others were
OL,8,Fexperiencing missing mail too.
OL,10,FThere are now calls for an
OL,11,Finvestigation.
OL,13,FRhian said: "It was my eldest son's
OL,14,Fbirthday in May, and I noticed that he
OL,15,Fhad fewer cards from relatives than
OL,16,Fhe'd normally have. We enquired with
OL,17,Frelatives and they said they're sent
OL,18,Fcards with money in them and they'd
OL,19,Fjust never turned up.
