OL,6,F"We waited a few weeks and nothing
OL,7,Farrived. At the time, I thought maybe
OL,8,Fit was just one of those things,
OL,9,Fthey'd maybe got lost in the post.
OL,11,F"A month later, it was my second son's
OL,12,Fbirthday and the same thing happened
OL,13,Fagain. None of the cards or money
OL,14,Farrived.
OL,16,F"It would have been around maybe #20
OL,17,Fin each card so probably about #40 to
OL,18,F#60 went missing altogether for each
OL,19,Fof them, so that would amount to about
OL,20,F#120."
