OL,4,Ccalls for Royal Mail investigation
OL,6,FShe complained to Royal Mail and was
OL,7,Ftold standard first and second-class
OL,8,Fitems aren't tracked so the matter
OL,9,Fcould not be investigated further. It
OL,10,Fis not known what happened and how the
OL,11,Fcards went missing.
OL,13,FBut she knew others had experienced
OL,14,Fsimilar issues so decided to share
OL,15,Fwhat had happened on a community
OL,16,FFacebook group, and was overwhelmed
OL,17,Fwith the response.
