OL,6,F"I was bombarded with messages," she
OL,7,Fsaid. "I received tens and tens of
OL,8,Fcomments by people in the local area
OL,9,Fsaying that money and cards were going
OL,10,Fmissing, particularly birthday cards
OL,11,Fand some were arriving opened and
OL,12,Fthings taken out of them."
OL,14,FAmong the comments on Facebook, people
OL,15,Fin the area claimed:
OL,17,FRhian and others in the town are now
OL,18,Fcalling for an investigation into the
OL,19,Fpostal system.
