OL,6,F"I'm sure our town is not the only
OL,7,Ftown this is happening in, they need
OL,8,Fto act on it now," Rhian said.
OL,10,FTo investigate the issue further, ITV
OL,11,FWales sent eight colourful birthday
OL,12,Fcards from various locations. Four of
OL,13,Fthe cards contained #5 notes.
OL,15,FSeven out of eight cards arrived at
OL,16,Ftheir intended destination, including
OL,17,Fthe cards containing money, but two
OL,18,Flooked damaged and one card went
OL,19,Fmissing completely.
