OL,3,CTown's missing birthday cards spark
OL,4,Ccalls for Royal Mail investigation
OL,6,FRoyal Mail declined an interview but a
OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "We acknowledge the
OL,8,Fresults of ITV Wales' own
OL,9,Finvestigation that confirmed all
OL,10,Fletters containing money arrived as
OL,11,Fintended.
OL,13,F"The process for delivering the
OL,14,Fmillions of letters that arrive
OL,15,Feveryday involves an entire network of
OL,16,Fletter drums and sorting machines
OL,17,Fwhich can occasionally result in
OL,18,Fclipping or minor damage to the
OL,19,Fenvelope as shown in their examples.
