OL,6,F"We publish guidance online for
OL,7,Fsending valuables, this includes
OL,8,Fsending letters via special delivery,
OL,9,Fmeasures such as packing any money
OL,10,Fsecurely to make it invisible from the
OL,11,Foutside and not indicating on the
OL,12,Fpackaging that money is enclosed.
OL,14,F"We take the security of mail very
OL,15,Fseriously and investigate any concerns
OL,16,Fraised by customers."
